headline.main: Futures Fall Amid North Korea Missiles, Trump Wiretap Talk
headline.print_headline: Futures Fall Amid North Korea Missiles, Trump Wiretap Talk

lead_paragraph: U.S. stock index futures fell on Sunday amid news of North Korea's firing of four ballistic missiles and President Donald Trump's accusation that his predecessor, Barack Obama, wiretapped him.
